title: An Update on the LIBOR Transition and Why It Matters for Wall Street and Main Street
description: Jason Granet, head of the firm’s LIBOR transition effort, gives an update on the timing and impact of the industry-wide transition away from the London Inter-bank Offered Rate (LIBOR).
